{"tid":315012,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"一日一好歌推介 周國賢離魂記","createTime":"2017-07-09T16:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T12:56:05.000Z","uid":68796,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db9a56740b0071352bd1c94a33dfad963fd7278a","tid":315012,"uid":68796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nlbDyUjkGgk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnlbDyUjkGgk&d=0MjafgSmdoTvJ4GhoGIKG%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=be34479b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nlbDyUjkGgk</a><br />\n由於呢首歌好似好少人識所以想特別推介下 梁柏堅嘅詞令到成首歌都都好有意境 講述面對女/男朋友嘅離去 叫人要灑脫釋懷 十分有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7602d5c0784387f25a2adde0efa61ee2ebabe67e","tid":315012,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:12:14.000Z","msg":"正皮 我都好鍾意個詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cf371573c1287d05d70b781cfd2957108080a1","tid":315012,"uid":68796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮 我都好鍾意個詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JHlp475dcf0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJHlp475dcf0&d=0MjafgSmdoTvJ4GhoGIKG%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d2a5cab8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JHlp475dcf0</a><br />\n介紹埋首兩首主題都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以去搵埋多首就三部曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同嘅係 dear Jane嗰首講嘅範圍廣啲<br />\n不過 離魂記嘅勉勵性 係呢首超越唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49878e433e4641fd08470a41615b49d2513dfc3d","tid":315012,"uid":2135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci